wiki.content: In “Spin Again”, Uzi talks about money, girls, jewelry, and also name-drops famous female rapper Ice Spice. This song was first previewed on the 26th of June at the famous BET Awards. This sparked some attention at Uzi for two major reasons. First reason: the song was censored, which made a lot of fans make videos about it on the popular app TikTok. Second reason: JT, Uzi’s girlfriend threw a phone at Uzi moments after performing this song. Uzi sat next to Ice Spice, who he name-dropped in this song, which made a lot of people think that JT threw the phone at him for the reason that he sat next to her. On June 28, 2023, just two days before the release of Pink Tape, Uzi would host a “Pink Prom” in promotion of the album and once again previewed this song. Read more on Last.fm.
